Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • client.app.interfaces.ScheduleObject
      • client.app.obj.User

  • public class User
extends ScheduleObject
    Class representing a user using the Application. Maintains all data about the user and their saved data after using the application. It's state is kept up to date in the LOCAL Database by the Client
